		<p>Whisk in a touch (1/4-1/2 tsp) of vanilla after the cream.  You can add flavoring oils for variety.  Raspberry, lemon, orange, for example, are also tasty in the right recipe.  Adding bittersweet chocolate is wonderful on ice cream, drizzled on cheesecake, fruit, or right off the spoon!</p>	
