	<div class="comment odd" id="c58916">
		<p>I make some caramel sauce like this but it adds balsamic vinegar.It's an Italian thing! This is how I do it:</p>

<p>1c heavy cream or 1/2 & 1/2<br />
1 cup sugar granulated<br />
2 TBS water<br />
4 Tbs balsamic vinegar<br />
1 lemon juiced<br />
1/2 tsp salt<br />
Dissolve sugar with 2 tbs water and cook for 8-9 minutes until dark golden. Carefully add cream to mixture stir, add lemon, vinegar and salt. EASY! Yummy!</p>

<p>I put it on ice cream or over baked apples.</p>	
