<p><em>Hi Dee,  margarine is nothing more than solidified vegetable oil with artificial flavoring.  It is completely different chemically than butter.  Personally I would not attempt to make caramel with margarine, as I seriously doubt it would turn out. If you do try it, please do let us know how it worked for you. ~Elise</em></p>	
